         <release version="3.3.0" date="2024-06-23">
  <url type="details">https://github.com/Daniele-rolli/Beaver-Notes/releases/tag/3.3.0</url>
<description>
  <p>Release description</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Bug Fixes:
      <ul>
        <li>Welcome Note (#184)</li>
        <li>Scroll Bar (#185)</li>
        <li>Tab Key Behavior (#195 & #197)</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <li>New Features:
      <ul>
        <li>Mermaid Block Integration</li>
        <li>Enhanced Code Block</li>
        <li>Custom Fonts</li>
        <li>Copy Button</li>
        <li>Improved File Block</li>
        <li>New Design</li>
        <li>Download Button</li>
        <li>Enhanced Callouts will now be inserted using ::color name</li>
        <li>Data API for Third-Party Integrations</li>
        <li>Collapsible Headings</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <li>Security and Privacy:
      <ul>
        <li>New Settings (Password & Integrations)</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <li>Improvements:
      <ul>
        <li>Improved Sync</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <li>Translations:
      <ul>
        <li>Updated translations for English, German, Italian, Dutch, Spanish, and Simplified Chinese</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <li>Design Enhancements:
      <ul>
        <li>Enhanced Toggles</li>
        <li>Improved Dialogs</li>
        <li>New Checkboxes</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
  </ul>
</description>
